h1 ru
p Welcome to ruBroker, a stock based game

h3 Stocks
form(data-bind='submit: buyStock')
  | Buy stock:
  input(data-bind='value: newStockText', placeholder='What stock do you wanna buy?')
  button(type='submit') Buy
ul(data-bind='foreach: stocks, visible: stocks().length > 0')
  li
    input(type='checkbox', data-bind='checked: isOwned')
    input(data-bind='value: name, disable: isOwned')
    a(href='#', data-bind='click: $parent.sellStock') Delete
| You have
b(data-bind='text: ownedStocks().length') Â 
|  stock(s)
span(data-bind='visible: ownedStocks().length == 0')  - it's time to start buying!
button(data-bind='click: save') Save

#messages
  input#text-input(type='text')
  input#send-button(type='button', value='Send')

script(type='text/javascript', src='/javascripts/rubroker.js')